  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0baa\u0baa\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u00a0 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b9c\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0baa\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Reverend Jeevanta Peiris filed a petition seeking to prevent his arrest",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A fundamental rights violation petition has been filed in the High Court today (2) on behalf of Aruth Father Jeevanta Peiris, who is known as the leading activist of the people's protest against the government.",
        "This petition has been filed seeking an order restraining his arrest.",
        "Western Province Senior Deputy Inspector General of Police Deshabandhu Thennakone, Inspector General of Police Chandana Wickramaratne, three army commanders, Attorney General and others have been named.",
        "Reverend Jeevanta Peiris has mentioned in his petition that those named as the defendants are planning to arrest him without any reasonable grounds or issues.",
        "Puripikkumar has claimed that his fundamental rights have been violated and has sought an interim order restraining his arrest till the case is investigated and adjudicated."
      ],
